===Etymology===
(1520) From {{term|beauty|lang=en}} + {{term|-ful||full of|lang=en}}. Displaced earlier {{term|sheen|lang=en}} (from {{etyl|enm|-}} {{term|schene||beautiful|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term/t|ang|scīene||beautiful}}), {{etyl|enm|-}} {{term|wliti||beautiful|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term/t|ang|wlitiġ||beautiful}}.

